snippet.title: Vigor – Xbox Series X|S Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Free Now on Xbox Series X|S

Outlive the apocalypse, Vigor is a free-to-play looter shooter in post-war Norway.

Shoot and loot in a tense encounters
Build your shelter and vital equipment
Challenge others in various game modes
Play on your own or fight together
